### 1. Owner สมัครใช้งาน (Register)
POST http://localhost:3000/owner/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner_name": "Owner",
  "contact_info": "0123456789",
  "email": "owner@gmail.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### 2. Owner ล็อกอิน (Login)
POST http://localhost:3000/owner/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner@gmail.com",
  "password": "SecurePass456!"
}

### 3. Owner อัปโหลด CSV
POST http://localhost:3000/owner/upload-csv
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="owners.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./path/to/owners.csv
--boundary--

### 4. Owner ขอ OTP สำหรับรีเซ็ตรหัสผ่าน
POST http://localhost:3000/owner/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "owner@gmail.com"
}

### 5. Owner ยืนยัน OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/owner/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "owner@gmail.com",
  "otp": "413529"
}

### 6. Owner เปลี่ยนรหัสผ่านใหม่
PATCH http://localhost:3000/owner/reset-password/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newPassword": "SecurePass456!"
}

### 7. Owner สร้าง Employee (ต้องแนบ Token)
POST http://localhost:3000/owner/create-employee
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "employee@example.com",
  "password": "EmployeePass123!"
}

### 8. Owner ดูข้อมูลตัวเอง
GET http://localhost:3000/owner/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
